reviewText: My 1 year old daughter loves this show! The music really gets her into it and I love that she's hearing Spanish as well. It's a lifesaver DVD when I want to distract her!
I recommend this dvd. A lot of nice songs! My daughter enjoys the songs everytime she watches it. I am so in love with the songs!!!

Our granddaughter loves Dora & is growing up, advancing to Dora & Friends. This makes watching her favorite characters while traveling - just perfect. She watched one DVD many times & it has now started to stall towards the end of the DVD. So far the 2nd one is fine.
My granddaughter loved it.
Purchased for girls ages 5 and 7, who love Dora but are just a bit old for the younger version. This was perfect and they love the older Dora, and all of the new songs.

Excellent price for the whole season! My daughter will be thrilled.
